data.description: Just a short drive to Key West, this elevated home offers 1404 sq ft of living space.  The open kitchen, dining and living room is ideal for entertaining.  The kitchen features stainless appliances, abundant cabinet space, & island with breakfast bar.  Tall 9ft ceilings, crown molding, central AC, large closets, hurricane windows and doors and more!  Primary bedroom offers a full en suite bath.  Hall bathroom and two additional bedrooms are spacious.  Full size laundry on main level.   Plenty of yard space, ample parking in driveway or the under home which has tall clearance, patio space for relaxing and storage.  Close to Calusa Beach, Key Deer Refuge Nature Center, Bahia Honda State Park, and more!  50X100 LOT. Low flood insurance cost with assumable policy!
